# 🔟 CROSS-FUNDING SOURCE CONTROL

If procurement uses:

* Donor funds
* Grant funds
* Restricted project funds

System enforces:

* Spending within funding agreement scope
* Category restrictions
* Reporting segregation

Prevents fund misuse.

