# 1️⃣1️⃣ BUDGET REALLOCATION WORKFLOW

If additional funds required:

```
Request Budget Adjustment
        ↓
Finance Review
        ↓
Approval or Rejection
        ↓
Budget Updated
```

All changes logged.

No manual override without audit record.

