# 1️⃣3️⃣ OVERSPENDING PROTECTION RULES

System blocks:

* Tender publication without budget
* Award exceeding reserved amount
* Amendment exceeding threshold
* Payment beyond committed value

Optional tolerance (e.g., 5%) configurable.

